        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H F Cs\"><math alttext=\"H F Cs\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>HFCs</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H C F Cs\"><math alttext=\"H C F Cs\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>HCFCs</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> are not classified as greenhouse gases but <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C F C s\"><math alttext=\"C F C s\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>CFCs</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> are.</p>",
